    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Since Java 8:</p>\n<pre><code>String.join(&quot;,&quot;, slist);\n</code></pre>\n<p>From Apache Commons library:</p>\n<pre><code>import org.apache.commons.lang3.StringUtils\n</code></pre>\n<p>Use:</p>\n<pre><code>StringUtils.join(slist, ',');\n</code></pre>\n<p>Another similar question and answer <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/63258/1651233\">here</a></p>\n"
