      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Well, I stand corrected.  Your right.  In your example you don&#39;t loop for each element in the string.  You literally just run against the length twice, which would be constant.  Way to keep me honest.  Keep up the good work."
