  "title" : "Best way to convert list to comma separated string in java",
  "body" : "<p>I have <code>Set&lt;String&gt; result</code> &amp; would like to convert it to comma separated string. My approach would be as shown below, but looking for other opinion as well.</p>\n\n<pre><code>List&lt;String&gt; slist = new ArrayList&lt;String&gt; (result);\nStringBuilder rString = new StringBuilder();\n\nSeparator sep = new Separator(\", \");\n//String sep = \", \";\nfor (String each : slist) {\n    rString.append(sep).append(each);\n}\n\nreturn rString;\n</code></pre>\n"
}